{"tid":2343644,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"TC Candler 全球百大帥哥、美女排行TOP1出爐！","createTime":"2020-12-28T05:56:15.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-28T09:47:53.000Z","uid":74065,"like":2,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":36,"replies":[{"pid":"7d988d8acf93d2444921af6f50292c60a68bdea5","tid":2343644,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-28T05:56:15.000Z","msg":"美國電影網站「TC Candler」每到年底都會公布「全球百大帥哥」與「全球百大美女」，28日名單出爐，「全球百大帥哥」今年由瑞典YouTuber「PewDiePie」菲利克斯（Felix Kjellberg）奪冠，去年的冠軍防彈少年團（BTS）柾國掉到第四名，同樣拿過該榜單冠軍的V，今年則是亞軍。「全球百大美女」前四名也有兩張亞洲臉孔，分別是第二名的Lisa和第四名的子瑜。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/5361/d5361527.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5361%2Fd5361527.jpg&h=8c86393c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲全球百大帥哥2020年冠軍，是瑞典YouTuber「PewDiePie」。（圖／翻攝自YouTube／TC Candler）<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/5361/d5361526.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5361%2Fd5361526.jpg&h=402c39a2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲全球百大帥哥2020年亞軍，防彈少年團V。（圖／翻攝自YouTube／TC Candler）<br />\n<br />\n「TC Candler」每到年底都會公布「全球百大帥哥」與「全球百大美女」，雖然之後不少網站或媒體也如法炮製，但「TC Candler」仍是較被網友認可的「真榜單」。先前「假榜單」盛傳拿下百大帥哥冠軍的大陸男星肖戰，則是第7名。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/5361/d5361524.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5361%2Fd5361524.jpg&h=02093edf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲先前「假榜單」盛傳拿下百大帥哥冠軍的大陸男星肖戰，則是第7名。（圖／翻攝自YouTube／TC Candler）<br />\n<br />\n2020年「全球百大美女」后冠是以色列女星雅兒謝爾比亞（Yael Shelbia），她是模特兒，同時也是女演員。前四名中的兩位亞洲臉孔，都是南韓女團中的「外國人」，分別是出身泰國的BLACKPINK成員Lisa拿到第二名，曾經拿下冠軍的TWICE子瑜，這回則是第四名。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/5361/d5361523.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5361%2Fd5361523.jpg&h=08cc37c6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲全球百大美女2020年冠軍，是以色列女星雅兒謝爾比亞。（圖／翻攝自YouTube／TC Candler）<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/5361/d5361529.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5361%2Fd5361529.jpg&h=990c2b0e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲全球百大帥哥2020年亞軍，是BLACKPINK成員Lisa。（圖／翻攝自YouTube／TC Candler）<br />\n<br />\n▲子瑜第四名。（圖／翻攝自YouTube／TC Candler）<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=vAo2GEa1a_I\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DvAo2GEa1a_I&d=%2BrTTj2V4oNsvrkryR3gjd6QEQZ%2FBMmOowG797g%2FgSDo%3D&h=112f7c82\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=vAo2GEa1a_I</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=GbaK1xs_9Lw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DGbaK1xs_9Lw&d=%2BrTTj2V4oNsvrkryR3gjd6QEQZ%2FBMmOowG797g%2FgSDo%3D&h=d80e665b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=GbaK1xs_9Lw</a>"},{"pid":"895cbcbfc265b6a5537a31d052a862ce8c152161","tid":2343644,"uid":178619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-28T05:57:20.000Z","msg":"汁?"},{"pid":"ec4d43942226a77c43d96ca343104aef8fd2d3ab","tid":2343644,"uid":74065,"like":3,"dislike":24,"score":-21,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-12-28T05:57:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qKOOO8O.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqKOOO8O.jpg&h=7538e3ed&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"24dcabd1f4d0b005864be6a948585d5b961fd2ce","tid":2343644,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"895cbcbfc265b6a5537a31d052a862ce8c152161","tid":2343644,"uid":178619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-28T05:57:20.000Z","msg":"汁?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-28T05:58:16.000Z","msg":"下面咪有片<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b7f4b3b952828d1fbf417113b248f0a37185d94","tid":2343644,"uid":33359,"like":2,"dislike":5,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-28T05:59:13.